sequenceDiagram
  participant Z as Zoho
  participant I as Ingestion (Lambda)
  participant Q as SQS/EventBridge
  participant A as Airflow
  participant W as Workers (Lambda)
  participant P as RDS Postgres
  participant S as S3
  participant M as SageMaker
  participant API as Data API (FastAPI)

  Z->>I: New data available / webhook / scheduled pull
  I->>S: Store raw payload (immutable)
  I->>P: Upsert minimal metadata (device_id, timestamps)
  I->>Q: Publish "raw_data_ready" event

  Q->>A: Trigger DAG (or A polls)
  A->>W: Run ETL job (container task)
  W->>S: Write curated/cleaned dataset snapshot
  W->>P: Write curated tables + quality stats

  A->>M: Trigger training / refresh (optional schedule)
  M->>S: Persist model artifacts + metrics
  M->>P: Register model version + lineage

  A->>W: Run forecast + goal seek
  W->>P: Write forecast_results / goal_seek_results
  W->>S: Write report files (csv/xlsx) + manifests

  API->>P: Serve forecasts/goal seek
  API->>S: Serve report download (presigned URL)